<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>全索引扫描并不一定就比全表扫描好，取决于数据存储位置。如果数据在内存，那么这两种没有太大区别。如果数据在磁盘，全表扫描比全索引扫描要好，这是因为，全表扫描是顺序读数据（顺序</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IO</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>），而全索引扫描是随机读取数据（随机</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IO</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>），可能会产生随机读</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>(reandom read)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。显然，顺序读要比随机读快很多</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>unique_subquery</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>和</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>index_subquery</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>虽然都存在使用索引优化，但默认情况下，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>MySQL </span><span
